snippet.title: OFFICIAL THE DIVISION 2 - WARLORDS OF NEW YORK - SEASON THREE OVERVIEW
snippet.description:
In Season 3, the manhunt continues when the Division realizes Bardon Schaeffer, the elusive leader of the Black Tusk’s BTSU, recruits four disavowed agents to form and lead a new rogue cell.
 The Division must now track down the high value target, Schaeffer, by neutralizing each of the rogue members of his cell and find out what exactly Schaeffer is plotting. 

Warlords of New York is now available on PC, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One.

http://thedivisiongame.com/buy
